{"tid":1885373,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"每日都飲酒，竟然可以活到 112 歲？？？","createTime":"2020-02-18T08:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T14:15:00.000Z","uid":123335,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"20e406d39faf184f0e8d5eeb5a84e4e55bb1e642","tid":1885373,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:49:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英最長壽人瑞112歲逝，養生竟靠威士忌</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n英國最長壽的人瑞葛蕾絲（Grace Jones），6月7日在位於伍斯特（Worcester）的家中，在睡夢裡安詳去世，她112年的生命中，見證了2次世界大戰、5次英國王位繼承以及26任首相更替。她每一年生日都獲得媒體高度關注，曾經在受訪時透露「養生秘訣」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我每一天晚上，都會喝一點威士忌摻水。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4164/d4164770.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4164%2Fd4164770.jpg&h=a1588c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Source: <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190614/1467019.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190614%2F1467019.htm&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=561c5832\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190614/1467019.htm</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解日日飲酒，都可以咁長命 ？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽講酒精好毒架喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一級致癌物黎"},{"pid":"599df02f6f6ff510f7be4f3aefc2caeb2467a5f6","tid":1885373,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"消毒"},{"pid":"4b3536b377c8ad67d6f2080e336ac5730a0edd2e","tid":1885373,"uid":187108,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:51:08.000Z","msg":"因為酒是故鄉濃"},{"pid":"46dcfa57c35edaf74caaacdf3022ddcac0841468","tid":1885373,"uid":22901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-