：木村 次郎右衛門／きむら じろうえもん Kimura Jirōemon，1897年4月19日－2013年6月12日），本名三宅 金治郎，日本長壽男性，超級人瑞，享高壽116歲54日。他入選了金氏世界紀錄，是人類史上最長壽男性，第一位無爭議活到116歲的男性, 也是最後一位逝世的生於19世紀的男性。<br />\n<br />\n木村自述並無特別的長壽秘方，只是飲食習慣較清淡、食量有節制且營養多樣化不偏食，木村特別喜歡吃紅豆餅與米飯，百歲之後的生日會愛吃烤魚。木村習慣吃八成飽，不抽菸，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只少量飲酒</span></strong>[3][4][5]。<br />\n<br />\n岩岩無聊 search 下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7bb3d6e8de548a83cb2244232387234c07f4a5","tid":1885373,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T09:23:44.000Z","msg":"我每日都飲4大罐啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f224410353ecc8919937a4181f4ff8b9449433e","tid":1885373,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f74ee2afad60e3a568f25fd8bb878bf27dbd9dc8","tid":1885373,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"889aba1ee0329329e81c45acd396f2906e0cdedc","tid":1885373,"uid":286017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"長壽既人飲酒=/=飲酒既人長壽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n腦係要用下既"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T09:10:18.000Z","msg":"個問題係 <br />\n點解佢日日飲都可以咁長命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"因為佢唔飲就會有130歲命<br />\n咁得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}